Package: pohoda-zabbix
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, php-cli (>= 8.1), php-vitexsoftware-digest-modules,
 php-vitexsoftware-pohoda-connector, zabbix-agent2 | zabbix-agent
Recommends: zabbix-agent2
Description: Zabbix monitoring for Pohoda accounting
 Business metrics monitoring for Pohoda accounting system using Zabbix.
 Collects data via shared digest modules through the Pohoda mServer API.
 .
 Monitored metrics include:
  - Debtors: company count, invoice count, overdue-age buckets (0-30, 31-60,
    61-90, 90+ days)
  - Outcoming and incoming invoice counts (total, active, cancelled)
  - Incoming and outgoing payment counts
  - Waiting income and waiting payments (count + total amount)
  - Unmatched bank payments (count + total amount)
  - Pohoda mServer connectivity status
 .
 The --period option selects the analysis window: month (default, last 30
 days), year (current calendar year), or a specific four-digit year.
 Results are cached per period for 5 minutes to reduce mServer load.
 Compatible with Zabbix Agent 2 (recommended) and Zabbix Agent.
